verses.roman:
vāsudeva-dattera ei murāri-guptera āra
buddhimanta-khāṅnera ei vividha prakāra

synonyms: vāsudeva-dattera—of Vāsudeva Datta; ei—these; murāri-guptera—of Murāri Gupta; āra—and; buddhimanta-khāṅnera—of Buddhimanta Khān; ei—these; vividha prakāra—of different varieties.
translation: "And all these varieties of food have been given by Vāsudeva Datta, Murāri Gupta and Buddhimanta Khān.
